,"primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"森田望智","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"","name":"Misato Morita","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Місато Моріта","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"森田望智 ，1996 年 9 月 13 日出生於神奈川縣，日本女性演員，所屬事務所為 Sony Music Artists。主要作品有《全裸導演》《人生 I 字路》等","name":"森田望智","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Мисато Морита","primary":false}}]}},"person_3445783_translations":{"at":1772689444958,"data":{"id":3445783,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"강채영","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Kang Chae-young","primary":false}}]}},"person_1174458_translations":{"at":1772689445092,"data":{"id":1174458,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Jie Yan is an actor.","name":"Yan Jie","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"言杰，原名延桀，演员，中华神武功夫团团长兼总教练。\n\n2005年，出演个人首部电视剧《汉武大帝》，从而正式进入演艺圈。2007年，参加选秀节目《龙的传人》并获得全国五强。2008年，参演情感剧《咏春》。2010年，参演历史剧《南下南下》；同年，参演动作片《截拳道》。2012年，主演了动作片《神算子蒋敬》；同年，参演战争剧《楚汉争雄》 。2013年，参演古装宫廷剧《御前侍卫》；同年，参演由徐克执导的悬疑动作片《狄仁杰之神都龙王》。2015年，因在古装谋权剧《琅琊榜》中饰演卓青遥一角而受到关注；11月，参演水浒系列电影《神行太保戴宗之夺命狂奔》。2016年，参演武侠剧《杜心五传奇》；同年，主演了年代剧《古城小女人》。","name":"言杰","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"Yan Jie","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Янь Цзе","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"言傑，原名延桀，演員，中華神武功夫團團長兼總教練。\n\n2005 年，出演個人首部電視劇《漢武大帝》，從而正式進入演藝圈。2007 年，參加選秀節目《龍的傳人》並獲得全國五強。2008 年，參演情感劇《詠春》。2010 年，參演歷史劇《南下南下》；同年，參演動作片《截拳道》。2012 年，主演了動作片《神算子蔣敬》；同年，參演戰爭劇《楚漢爭雄》 。2013 年，參演古裝宮廷劇《禦前侍衞》；同年，參演由徐克執導的懸疑動作片《狄仁傑之神都龍王》。2015 年，因在古裝謀權劇《琅琊榜》中飾演卓青遙一角而受到關注；11 月，參演水滸系列電影《神行太保戴宗之奪命狂奔》。2016 年，參演武俠劇《杜心五傳奇》；同年，主演了年代劇《古城小女人》。","name":"言傑","primary":false}}]}},"person_146869_translations":{"at":1772689451581,"data":{"id":146869,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Eriko Sato (佐藤 江梨子 Satō Eriko, born December 19, 1981) is a Japanese actress. She is also a former gravure idol and made her debut in 1998.","name":"Eriko Sato","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IT","iso_639_1":"it","name":"Italiano","english_name":"Italian","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"佐藤江梨子","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"佐藤江梨子（Eriko Sato，1981年12月19日-），日本女演员。她也是前凹版偶像，并于1998年出道。","name":"佐藤江梨子","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"","name":"Eriko Sató","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Еріко Сато","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"（佐藤江梨子，1981 年 12 月 19 日-），日本女演員。她也是前凹版偶像，並於 1998 年出道。","name":"佐藤江梨子","primary":false}}]}},"person_4848613_translations":{"at":1772689454732,"data":{"id":4848613,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","d